<div class="content">
    <h2>Key Offroad Terms</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Suspension Lift:</strong> Increases ground clearance by raising the suspension.</li>
        <li><strong>Gearing Ratio:</strong> Affects vehicle performance and torque for offroad conditions.</li>
        <li><strong>All-Terrain Tires:</strong> Tires designed for both on-road and offroad use.</li>
    </ul>
